{"type": "article", "id": 13580, "title": "柳杉工具盒子", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-17T07:55:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122447kWCPZ0BE7UNGlKI6.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本优质工具品牌 Best Made Co 最近推出了一个叫做 “Japanese Cedar Carpenter’s Box” 的工具盒子，采用柳杉制作而成，兼具简洁的设计和精巧的工匠手艺。盒子平面抽拉门平滑稳定，无缝防水。同时，盒子进行了抗菌防虫处理，避免盒子受潮或者久置后遭遇细菌蚊虫的侵袭。同时，因为所用木材纹理的区别，每一只盒子都是世界上独一无二的。<a href=\"http://www.bestmadeco.com/collections/this-week-at-best-made/products/japanese-cedar-carpenters-box#product-tab\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141320vdxVEDnkWgBmrMZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141320dwh5ovJHyjCefOFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413215dHFMuTQtC7eBgwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141321BwCPaWfU7Lx6NZ38.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}